This is my new favorite Middle Eastern place to eat.
First off the dining room and restroom were spotless clean.
We ordered a beef kabob plate and a gyro sandwich with fries.
The food came out quick and piping hot.First off lets talk about the kabob plate.
It was a very large portion of seasoned ground beef cooked on a flat skewer.
